<article class="post">
  <div class="title">
    <a href="{{post_url}}" target="_blank" id="post-title">{{title}}</a>
    <span>({{post_url}})</span>
  </div>
  <div class="meta">
    {{vote_count}} point(s) by {{user.username}} on {{created_at}}
    |
    <a href="/post/{{id}}">{{comments.length}} comment(s)</a>
  </div>
</article>
        {{!-- When we pass the post object into the partial, 
        we don't pass the object as is but rather pass in all of the properties of that object. --}}